PrecisSetting apart of (a) some 965 hectares of land, mines and minerals included and 0.4 hectares of mines and mineral only, situated in Saskatchewan, for the use and benefit of the PIAPOT BAND as Piapot Cree First Nation Indian Reserve No. 75 "I", and (b) some 2.5 hectares of mines and minerals only, as an addition to Piapot Cree First Nation Indian Reserve No. 75 "J".
